- Aku bisa jalan sendiri.

683
00:46:16,191 --> 00:46:17,818
Jangan bergerak-gerak.

684
00:46:18,152 --> 00:46:19,236
Pecundang.

685
00:46:20,112 --> 00:46:21,905
Kenapa gadis itu begitu penting?

686
00:46:40,924 --> 00:46:41,884
Eugene.

687
00:46:44,178 --> 00:46:45,179
Tuan!

688
00:46:48,098 --> 00:46:49,808
Lihat Danau Surga di Gunung Paektu?

689
00:46:49,892 --> 00:46:51,852
Tinggi dan jauh.

690
00:46:51,935 --> 00:46:53,145
Meletus tiga tahun lalu.

691
00:46:53,228 --> 00:46:55,481
- Bukan main.
- Wah.

692
00:46:55,564 --> 00:46:57,941
Jadi, kami tidak ke sana. Berbahaya.

693
00:46:58,025 --> 00:46:59,443
Begitu rupanya.

694
00:47:02,071 --> 00:47:03,530
Itu untuk Do-mi.

695
00:47:04,740 --> 00:47:06,075
Begitu...

